    <item>
      <title>KKR 如何帮助摩根大通在私人信贷方面取得关键胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/how-kkr-helped-jpmorgan-seal-a-key-victory-over-private-credit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年首次考虑以约 50 亿美元的债务收购医疗保健科技公司 Cotiviti Inc. 的交易时，该交易有望成为私人信贷公司有史以来提供的规模最大的此类融资。它现在被列为传统华尔街对抗直接贷款机构的最大胜利之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/how-kkr-helped-jpmorgan-seal-a-key-victory-over-private-credit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 15:06:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德的博伊文：通货膨胀将在今年晚些时候反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-22/inflation-will-rebound-later-in-year-blackrock-s-boivin-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德投资研究所(BlackRock Investment Institute)负责人让·博伊文(Jean Boivin)表示，美国通胀率将达到美联储2%的目标，但将在今年晚些时候反弹。博伊文在彭博电视台发表讲话时还表示，股市面临着一个“棘手”的宏观环境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-22/inflation-will-rebound-later-in-year-blackrock-s-boivin-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 15:04:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储杰斐逊警告称，为改善通胀而采取过多宽松政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/fed-s-jefferson-warns-of-easing-too-much-on-improving-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储副主席菲利普·杰斐逊周四表示，美联储需要警惕因通胀下降而过度降息，以免破坏物价稳定最终目标的实现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/fed-s-jefferson-warns-of-easing-too-much-on-improving-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿联酋航空任命两名高管作为克拉克的潜在继任者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/emirates-sets-up-two-executives-as-potential-successors-to-clark</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿联酋航空将两名高级管理人员提拔为总裁蒂姆·克拉克 (Tim Clark) 领导下的副职，在公司资深人士之间展开竞争，以接替领导这家迪拜航空公司二十年的 74 岁英国人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/emirates-sets-up-two-executives-as-potential-successors-to-clark</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 14:50:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国制造业活动以 2022 年以来最快速度扩张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/us-manufacturing-activity-expands-at-fastest-pace-since-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在订单增长强劲的推动下，美国制造业活动以 2022 年 9 月以来最快的速度扩张，这表明生产商正在摆脱长期低迷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/us-manufacturing-activity-expands-at-fastest-pace-since-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 14:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
