      <title>Nvidia 市值跃升近 2500 亿美元，刷新元记录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/nvidia-to-top-meta-record-with-nearly-250-billion-value-jump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英伟达公司 (Nvidia Corp.) 有望超越 Meta Platforms Inc. 历史性的股市表现，而距离 Facebook 所有者创下纪录仅三周。]]></description>
