    <item>
      <title>劳埃德银行承诺在收取 4.5 亿英镑汽车融资费用后回购股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/lloyds-takes-450-million-provision-for-car-finance-review</link>
      <description><![CDATA[劳埃德银行集团 (Lloyds Banking Group Plc) 拨出 4.5 亿英镑（5.7 亿美元）用于支付可能的赔偿和与汽车金融相关的其他费用，成为第一家对英国监管机构的审查标价的主要银行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/lloyds-takes-450-million-provision-for-car-finance-review</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 07:29:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着英伟达推动股市上涨，股市多头重新押注人工智能：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于英伟达公司的稳健前景重新点燃了人工智能热潮，而制造业数据增强了人们对美国经济的信心，股市延续了牛市走势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 23:05:32 GMT</pubDate>
